# Component Conventions

## Naming

- **Files:** kebab-case (`log-card.tsx`, `dashboard-sidebar.tsx`)
- **Exports:** PascalCase named exports — no default exports
- **Props:** interface named `ComponentNameProps`

## Structure

- Add `"use client"` only when the component uses hooks or browser APIs
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional/merged Tailwind classes

## Shared Types — Never Duplicate

Import from `@/types/dashboard` — never define these locally:

`Athlete`, `Role`, `SessionItem`, `TrainingSlot`, `TrainingSlotItem`,
`ReviewStatus`, `ReviewStatusFilterValue`, `LogEntry`, `Member`, `AttendanceStatus`

## Reusable Components — Use Instead of Inlining

| Pattern | Use this component |
|---------|--------------------|
| Delete/leave/remove confirmation | `DeleteConfirmDialog` from `@/components/ui/delete-confirm-dialog` |
| Log visibility badge (Shared/Private) | `VisibilityBadge` from `@/components/dashboard/shared/visibility-badge` |
| Tag pills in log cards/details | `TagPill` from `@/components/dashboard/shared/tag-pill` |

## Example

```tsx
"use client";

import { cn } from "@/lib/utils";
import type { Athlete } from "@/types/dashboard";

interface MyComponentProps {
  athletes: Athlete[];
  className?: string;
}

export function MyComponent({ athletes, className }: MyComponentProps) {
  return <div className={cn("rounded-lg p-4", className)}>...</div>;
}
```
